The teenage girlfriend of alleged East London hitman Bonga Skolpati gave the Mthatha High Court a spine-chilling account of how her boyfriend allegedly shot dead a popular Coffee Bay deputy principal in 2015. The evidence of Yolanda Ntshuntshe, 18, put Skolpati, 23, at the scene of 49-year-old Kholisile Baleni s murder.For the full story get a copy of the Dispatch or subscribe to our e-Edition for the complete newspaper with jobs, classifieds, crosswords, TV schedules and back editions